text: Yusof Ishak (12 August 191023 November 1970) was the first President of Singapore from 1965 to 1970. Ishak died while in office on 23 November 1970 from heart failure at the age of 60. ==References== Category:Presidents of Singapore Category:1910 births Category:1970 deaths Category:Deaths from heart failure
title: Yusof Ishak
